{"tid":645753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇咩事真係唔好夏天溝女","createTime":"2018-04-28T12:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T12:52:17.000Z","uid":117758,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"08301761a77b4e2f9a4e95189c25c0517f75f426","tid":645753,"uid":117758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"[專登係暑假之前出post]<br />\nDllm ，係香港想約約女出街，唔係行街睇戲就係食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n話說冬天由聖誕節，新年，去到情人節條街都有特別野行，有特別野睇。凍凍地，又見到大家著返啲靚衫，個feel幾舒服<br />\n見佢凍，拖一拖，攬一攬，<del>搞一搞</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係！</span><br />\n<br />\n夏天到就真係吊出聲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1）條街..悶撚到仆街<br />\n     夏天有咩假，用清明重陽放假約佢已經係on9架啦，男人要諗理由出街已經難，成條街大陸人多過香港人，乜mood都收返啦。熱撚到hihi要焗住同條女去行成堆大陸人嘅賣貴價貨嘅商場。10年後香港人想溝女係咪要淪落到行周生_ 同 萬_<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2）著衫永遠Tshirt加短褲，條女一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n      夏天除咗有腳睇我諗唔到有咩好處。件衫褲除咗遮住碌9仲有咩用你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔好睇，留唔到特別impression比人。夏天本身成身都好易出汗，一唔小心hi佢，濕到搞到大家都唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇一年四季都溝到女嘅ching教一教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006f0f8f75723aa87714cd275e3e65bcf1977e08","tid":645753,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"靚仔既著白tee都好charm啦 講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce2ac921d15b37112df702ae35db866343c7b3c","tid":645753,"uid":117758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"006f0f8f75723aa87714cd275e3e65bcf1977e08","tid":645753,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"靚仔既著白tee都好charm啦 講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:29:20.000Z","msg":"真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04f97c11e97152b46eee3c2618502dff71a8d58","tid":645753,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"第二點認同<br />\n唔同你第一點講咩"},{"pid":"40a35db07836ff4f6bf21f873518ee6a5fa202b7","tid":645753,"uid":117758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04f97c11e97152b46eee3c2618502dff71a8d58","tid":645753,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"第二點認同<br />\n唔同你第一點講咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"香港跟本就冇野行"},{"pid":"749cdbdea9a065dfd4509a67d96314e2f8f0676c","tid":645753,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55ca74f62c6930f1f91465d07e9a09aa32c0c4f","tid":645753,"uid":117758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749cdbdea9a065dfd4509a67d96314e2f8f0676c","tid":645753,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40a35db07836ff4f6bf21f873518ee6a5fa202b7","tid":645753,"uid":117758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d04f97c11e97152b46eee3c2618502dff71a8d58","tid":645753,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"第二點認同<br />\n唔同你第一點講咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"香港跟本就冇野行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"冬天都叫有啲題材， christmas 裝飾 睇下相叫下春咁"},{"pid":"5b9165158632240d3be533b8bbafc8b2ec369281","tid":645753,"uid":173011,"